         <abstract>
            <p>An attainable bound for the infinity norm of the inverse of a whole class of symmetric circulant Toeplitz matrices is found. The class of matrices includes those arising from interpolation with both odd and even degree periodic polynomial splines on a uniform mesh.</p>
